title: Check Out The Top Five Moments Of Dragon Ball Super From 2016
text:
Check Out The Top Five Moments Of Dragon Ball Super From 2016 Megan Peters Start Slideshow Slide of 
It has been a busy year for Dragon Ball Super . The long-awaited anime series finally debuted in 2015, and it continued its unstoppable takeove r well into the next year. In 2016, Toei Animation saw Dragon Ball Super go toe-to-toe with One Piece to become one of Japan’s most popular anime series - and it is time us fans celebrated. 
Here at ComicBook.com, we are looking back and taking note of Dragon Ball Super ’s best five moments. So, take a break and climb in our Capsule Corp time-machine; We’ve got Super Saiyans to look after. (Photo: Toei Animation )
